# Tsurai, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Tsurai (; Dargwa: Цурагӏи) is a rural locality (a selo) in Tsizgarinsky Selsoviet, Dakhadayevsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. The population was 189 as of 2010.
Geography
Tsurai is located 15&nbsp;km northeast of Urkarakh (the district's administrative centre) by road. Tsizgari and Kanasiragi are the nearest rural localities.
